# Data & security

Schema: @docs/DATA_MODEL.md

- Tables: `songs`, `sessions`, `weekly_reflections`, `coach_messages`.
- RLS on every table from day one. Service role server-side only; middleware on private routes.
- Never expose service role or Anthropic keys to the client.
- Public `(public)/` routes must not query or render private practice data.
- `songs.is_shared` drives future public home sync (Phase 4).
